  "description": "Rebirth looks different for everyone. \nWhich is why every detail of this ring is yours to choose.\n\nIf your transformation was forged in fire — choose the Ruby. Carried by royals into battle for centuries, believed to protect the heart and fortify the spirit. Yours to set in Oval, the cut that draws out its deepest, most saturated colour.\n\nIf your strength was built quietly, under enormous pressure — choose the Diamond. Each one brilliant. Each one earned.\n\nIf you move through the world with permanence — choose 18k Gold. If you carry your edge with restraint — choose Sterling Silver.\n\nEmerald cut for the one who is precise and deliberate. Oval for the one who flows. Cushion for the one who has learned that softness is not weakness.\n\nThe Memento Mori is not a ring you pick off a shelf. It is a ring you build — around your story, your stone, your metal, your moment.\n.\n[ brand, jewellery, custom design, custom jewellery, design, notred, scars, diamonds ]\n#brand #jewellery #design #notred #diamond",
